title: Crash report on startup
body:
I have installed Mumble on my computer several times, uninstalled, cleaned the registry and reinstalled, and every time I try to launch the program, the crash report shows up without it even launching. I am running WINDOWS7 HOME PREMIUM 64, Inter(R) Core(TM) i5-3570k CPU @ 3.40GHz, 8GB of RAM. I have tried running it as adiministrator, and still achieve the same results.


*This ticket has been migrated from sourceforge. It is thus missing some details like original creator etc.
The original is at https://sourceforge.net/p/mumble/bugs/1030/ .*
